  "text": "On the outer part of the barrier, the sedimentation was dominated by the deposition of shallow-benthic foraminifers and molluscs. In the sections studied, we only observe fossils and lithologies indicating the inner ramp to the middle ramp. Foraminifers observed such as orbitolites indicate the presence of seagrass and mud-free substrates [CITATION_1] .",
